---
import { Globe, MapPin, ArrowRight } from '@lucide/astro'
import Watermark from '../../Watermark.astro'
---

<section
  id='servicios'
  class='relative overflow-hidden py-24 md:py-32'
  style="background: linear-gradient(160deg, color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-cream) 85%, white) 0%, var(--color-cream) 50%, color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-cream) 85%, var(--color-surface)) 100%);">

  <div
    class='pointer-events-none absolute inset-0'
    aria-hidden='true'>
  </div>

  <Watermark text="SEO" position="top-right" opacity={4} size="4xl" class="text-white/40" />

  <div class='pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-px bg-gradient-fade-sage' aria-hidden='true'></div>
  <div class='pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-px bg-gradient-fade-sage-sm' aria-hidden='true'></div>

  <div class='relative mx-auto max-w-[860px] px-5'>

    <div class='mb-12'>
      <div data-animate class='mb-4'>
        <h2 class='text-xs font-bold text-base'>ESPECIALISTA SEO EN BARCELONA</h2>
      </div>
      <p data-animate class='font-heading text-h2 font-normal leading-tight tracking-tight text-base'>
        Esto es lo que hago para que te <span class="text-sage">llamen más.</span>
      </p>
      <div data-animate class='mt-6 flex items-center'>
        <div class='h-px w-32 bg-gradient-fade-base'></div>
        <div class='h-px w-10 bg-base/50'></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class='flex flex-col gap-4'>

      <a
        href='/posicionamiento-web-barcelona/'
        data-animate
        class='group relative flex flex-col sm:flex-row rounded-2xl border border-surface/10 border-l-0 border-t-0 border-b-0 bg-base overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5 shadow-card'
        >

        <div class='relative overflow-hidden bg-sage sm:w-[42%] shrink-0 px-6 py-7 flex flex-col justify-between gap-5 min-h-[160px] sm:min-h-0'>

          <svg class='pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 w-full h-full' aria-hidden='true' preserveAspectRatio='none'>
            <line x1='55%' y1='0%' x2='100%' y2='100%' stroke='rgba(250,234,177,0.08)' stroke-width='1' />
          </svg>

          <div class='relative flex items-center gap-3'>
            <div class='flex size-7 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-sage-10 border-sage-30'>
              <Globe aria-hidden='true' class='size-4 text-cream' />
            </div>
            <span class='text-xs font-bold uppercase text-cream-50'>Visibilidad en buscadores</span>
          </div>

          <div class='relative flex items-baseline gap-2'>
            <span class='text-h6 leading-none tabular-nums shrink-0 font-heading text-cream-30'>01</span>
            <h3 class='font-heading text-base font-semibold tracking-tight leading-snug text-white'>Posicionamiento Web en Barcelona</h3>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class='hidden sm:flex flex-col items-center justify-center w-px relative shrink-0'>
          <div class='absolute inset-y-0 left-0 w-px bg-surface/10'></div>
          <div class='relative z-10 size-2 rounded-full opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300 bg-sage' aria-hidden='true'></div>
        </div>

        <div class='flex flex-col justify-between gap-5 p-6 flex-1 bg-base'>
          <p class='text-base font-light text-cream'>
            Reviso tu web, la arreglo y la optimizo para que Google la muestre cuando alguien busca tu oficio en Barcelona.
          </p>
          <div class='flex items-center gap-2 text-base font-semibold text-cream transition-all duration-200 group-hover:gap-3'>
            Ver servicio →
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a
        href='/seo-local-barcelona/'
        data-animate
        class='group relative flex flex-col sm:flex-row rounded-2xl border border-surface/10 border-l-0 border-t-0 border-b-0 bg-base overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5 shadow-card'
        >

        <div class='relative overflow-hidden bg-sage sm:w-[42%] shrink-0 px-6 py-7 flex flex-col justify-between gap-5 min-h-[160px] sm:min-h-0'>

          <svg class='pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 w-full h-full' aria-hidden='true' preserveAspectRatio='none'>
            <line x1='55%' y1='0%' x2='100%' y2='100%' stroke='rgba(250,234,177,0.08)' stroke-width='1' />
          </svg>

          <div class='relative flex items-center gap-3'>
            <div class='flex size-7 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-cream-10 border-cream-20'>
              <MapPin aria-hidden='true' class='size-4 text-cream' />
            </div>
            <span class='text-xs font-bold uppercase text-cream-50'>Visibilidad en Google Maps</span>
          </div>

          <div class='relative flex items-baseline gap-2'>
            <span class='text-h6 leading-none tabular-nums shrink-0 font-heading text-cream-30'>02</span>
            <h3 class='font-heading text-base font-semibold tracking-tight leading-snug text-white'>SEO Local en Barcelona</h3>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class='hidden sm:flex flex-col items-center justify-center w-px relative shrink-0'>
          <div class='absolute inset-y-0 left-0 w-px bg-surface/10'></div>
          <div class='relative z-10 size-2 rounded-full opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300 bg-cream' aria-hidden='true'></div>
        </div>

        <div class='flex flex-col justify-between gap-5 p-6 flex-1 bg-base'>
          <p class='text-base font-light text-cream'>
            Optimizo tu ficha de Google Maps para que aparezcas entre los primeros cuando buscan tu servicio cerca y te llamen directamente.
          </p>
          <div class='flex items-center gap-2 text-base font-semibold text-cream transition-all duration-200 group-hover:gap-3'>
            Ver servicio →
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>